{"story":{"group_1":[{"bgm":"bgm01_anime03","nameNarration":"月夜","narration":"之后，在与月咲的交谈中，@我知道了父亲在一个叫做@天音竹工房的地方当工匠","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"我也知道自己@曾经的姓氏是“天音”"},{"narration":"我们知道了彼此的存在，@便如堤坝决堤般@不约而同地开始聊起自己的事"},{"bg":"bg_adv_12052.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"月夜","nameRight":"月咲","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"真是难以置信！"},{"chara":[{"id":101801}],"textLeft":"就连周末也要@一刻不停地进行练习！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":101801}],"textLeft":"当然，她想要重视身为水名女子@的名誉的心情，"},{"chara":[{"id":101801}],"textLeft":"我也是在那个环境中成长的，@并不是不明白。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"但是，有必要为此@将真实的我摧毁吗！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101801}],"textLeft":"老说什么水名水名水名的，@烦死了！"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"嗯嗯。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"拜这个所赐，@我都从没有去玩过。"},{"chara":[{"id":101801}],"textLeft":"就算周围的人都很尊敬我。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101801}],"textLeft":"但却完全没人能成为我的朋友！"},{"chara":[{"id":101801,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"你懂这种寂寞的感觉吗！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":1}],"textRight":"嗯嗯，我知道！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101901}],"textRight":"没想到我们连这点都很像呢。"},{"nameNarration":"月夜","narration":"或许是我们都很忙碌，@又或许是因为双胞胎的缘故，@我不确定其中的缘由","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"但月咲对我而言，@是第一个能让我滔滔不绝@说出自己真心话的人"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"天音","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101801}],"textLeft":"真想下次能再见到你，@和你说说话。"},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"别叫得这么生分啦。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"诶？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"好吗，月夜。"},{"chara":[{"id":101801}],"textLeft":"啊……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"好的，月咲！"},{"nameNarration":"月夜","narration":"就这样，@我们交换了联络方式，@以便今后见面","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21173.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"为了防止让双亲知道我们的事，@电话里存的是别的名字"},{"narration":"和笛子一样合而为一"},{"narration":"一个“○”形的满月印记"},{"bgm":"stop","narration":"但是，这种蜜月般的时光@并没有持续太久","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":100,"pos":1,"soulGem":0,"voice":"vo_char_1018_00_04","textHome":"由父亲手中所得的笛子，有着特殊的意义。"}],"nameCenter":"月夜","textCenter":"父亲给我们的笛子里，@有其他意义。","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":101801}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}